data.name: GAUZE ROLLS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% Cotton fabric

## STERILIZATION
- Non Sterile, Ethylene oxide and Steam Sterilization

## PRESENTATIONS
- Sterile and non-sterile

## PERFORMANCE
- Highly Absorbent
- Straight Edges

## AVAILABLE SPECIFICATIONS
- Cotton Yarn: 40s / 36s / 32s / 21s
- Mesh: 40x40 / 40x30 / 32x28 / 30x28, 30x36 / 30x20 / 28x26 / 26x24 / 20x12 / 19x15 / 19x11 / 11x8
- Width: 90cm (36″), 120cm (48″), 130cm (51″)
- Length:10m, 25m, 50m, 100yards (91m), 1000m, 2000m, 3000m
- MOQ: 5.000mts
- Color: white (mostly), green, blue
- Type: sterile or non-sterile x-ray detectable or not
- Woven way: plain
- Layer: 1ply / 2ply / 4ply / 8ply
